{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-transformer-remark-plaintext","description":"Creates a new graphql field `plainText` on every MarkdownRemark node","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-transform-remark"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"entr","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/9655d76c160c25c4e9f5f779aa8aa56e"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/entr/gatsby-transformer-remark-plaintext"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"description\"><a href=\"#description\" aria-label=\"description permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description</h2>\n<p>This is <strong>NOT</strong> a replacement of the official <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-transformer-remark/\"><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code></a> plugin. It just creates a new graphql field <code class=\"language-text\">plainText</code> on every MarkdownRemark node using the <a href=\"https://github.com/remarkjs/strip-markdown\"><code class=\"language-text\">strip-markdown</code></a> remark plugin.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">plainText</code> will contain simple paragraphs without formatting. Alt text will be used to replace images.</p>\n<h3 id=\"dependencies\"><a href=\"#dependencies\" aria-label=\"dependencies permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Dependencies</h3>\n<p>Gatsby 2.x</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-transformer-remark/\"><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-install\"><a href=\"#how-to-install\" aria-label=\"how to install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install --save gatsby-transformer-remark-plaintext</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"when-do-i-use-this-plugin\"><a href=\"#when-do-i-use-this-plugin\" aria-label=\"when do i use this plugin permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>When do I use this plugin?</h2>\n<p>You might find it useful for creating JSON-LD for Structured Data or other meta based on your markdown sources. </p>\n<h2 id=\"examples-of-usage\"><a href=\"#examples-of-usage\" aria-label=\"examples of usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples of usage</h2>\n<p>In <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> after <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark-plaintext`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Restart <code class=\"language-text\">$ gatsby develop</code>.</p>\n<p>Now you can add the <code class=\"language-text\">plainText</code> field to your queries.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query-for-data\"><a href=\"#how-to-query-for-data\" aria-label=\"how to query for data permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query for data</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\"><pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allMarkdownRemark<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">limit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        frontmatter <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          title\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        html\n        plainText\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-transformer-remark-plaintext/","id":"a99c11ab-5b47-5bb0-b885-14380fab561d","layout":"plugins"}}